title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Jordan/Gleeman/Layden/Birk!
description: Wild coach Bruce Boudreau opens up the show, former Vikings TE Steve Jordan joins, Gleeman in studio, Wolves GM Scott Layden calls in, Matt Birk and the Birk Bit, and Mike Zimmer's presser ends a full show!
